2. KPIs Dashboard Financeiro Consolidado (Hotelaria Pro)
KPIs Primários (Sempre Visíveis)
text
CORE 5 (RevPAR Framework):
├── 1. RevPAR (Revenue Per Available Room) = ADR × Ocupação
├── 2. ADR (Average Daily Rate) = Receita Quartos / Quartos Vendidos
├── 3. Ocupação % = Quartos Ocupados / Quartos Disponíveis
├── 4. GOPPAR (Gross Operating Profit Per Available Room)
└── 5. TRevPAR (Total Revenue Per Available Room)

KPIs Secundários (Cards Expandíveis):
├── Market Penetration Index (MPI) vs concorrentes
├── Channel Mix % (Direto vs OTAs)
├── Cancellations Rate < 15%
├── Length of Stay (Noites Média)
├── Ancillary Revenue % (F&B, Spa)
├── Cost per Occupied Room (CPOR)
└── Labor Cost % of Revenue < 35%
3. Integração PMS + Pagamentos (Arquitetura de Dados)
text
FLUXO DADOS RSV360 → DASHBOARD FINANCEIRO

1. PMS (MOD_004) → Postgres Reservations Table
   reservation.created_at
   reservation.checkin/checkout  
   reservation.total
   reservation.nights
   reservation.room_type
   reservation.source (DIRECT/OTA/VOICE)

2. Pagamentos (MOD_009) → Stripe Webhook
   payment_intent.succeeded → UPDATE reservation.status = 'PAID'
   stripe.charge.amount → financial_metrics.daily_revenue

3. OTAs (MOD_006) → Reconciliação
   ota_pull → reservation.external_id
   ota_commission → reservation.ota_commission

4. CRM WhatsApp (MOD_013) → Guest Data
   customer.phone → reservation.guest_phone
   interaction.type → upsell_opportunities

SQL VIEW CONSOLIDADA:
```sql
CREATE VIEW financial_kpis AS
SELECT 
  r.hotel_id,
  DATE(r.checkin) as date,
  COUNT(r.id) as reservations,
  SUM(r.total) as revenue,
  SUM(r.total - COALESCE(r.ota_commission, 0)) as net_revenue,
  AVG(r.total::numeric / r.nights) as adr,
  COUNT(r.id)::float / 150.0 as occupancy_rate, -- 150 quartos
  (SUM(r.total) / 150.0)::numeric as revpar,
  (SUM(r.total - COALESCE(r.ota_commission, 0)) / 150.0)::numeric as goppar
FROM reservations r 
WHERE r.status IN ('PAID', 'CHECKED_IN')
  AND r.checkin >= NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days'
GROUP BY r.hotel_id, DATE(r.checkin)
